# .eggshellfmtignore -- files/globs that `eggshell-fmt` (Meta/EggShellFmt) must NOT touch.
# gitignore-style syntax: one glob per line, `#` comments, `!` negates, trailing `/` = directory.
#
# eggshell-fmt ALSO reads .fantomasignore, and always skips obj/, bin/, _autogenerated_/,
# node_modules/, .git/, and *.fs.js -- so build output and vendored source are already excluded.
# Add project-specific opt-outs below.
#

# Generated Fable output tree (copied third-party + compiled .fs; never our source).
**/.build/
# Examples:
#   SuiteLegacy/                         # never reformat a whole suite
#   LibClient/src/Rn/Styles/Legacy/      # a subtree kept in its old shape
#   **/Generated.fs                      # a generated file by name, anywhere
#   !LibClient/src/Rn/Styles/Legacy/New.fs   # ...but do format this one
